Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:06.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(534,322)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.95,0:01:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  同学们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, class
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.43,0:01:06.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静  安静
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:06.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,quiet, quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.42,0:01:08.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请大家拿出纸笔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:08.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, get out your pencils and paper
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.71,0:01:10.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记下作业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:10.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and write down the assignment
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.45,0:01:13.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你听见了没
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:13.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.02,0:01:14.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们有作业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:14.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We get an assignment
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.78,0:01:16.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人必须写一篇作文
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:16.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone must write an essay
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.44,0:01:19.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主题是红绿灯前不能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:19.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on what not to do at a stoplight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:19.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1168,614)}红绿灯
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.49,0:01:21.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你听见了没
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:21.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.80,0:01:23.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,红绿灯前不能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:23.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What not to do at a stoplight
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.98,0:01:26.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不少于八百字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:26.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In no less than 800 words
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.34,0:01:29.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你听见了没
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:29.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.30,0:01:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八百字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,800 words?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.02,0:01:32.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:32.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.58,0:01:35.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天上交
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:35.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Due tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.05,0:01:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们记住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:36.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And remember, class
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认真做  不能偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,work hard and no goofing off
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.00,0:01:41.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:41.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.27,0:01:42.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:42.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no goofing off
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.87,0:01:46.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要写出史上最佳的作文
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:46.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am about to write the greatest essay of all time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.17,0:01:48.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟诸多佳作一样  这篇作文得写在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:48.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like most great essays it will be written
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纸上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on paper
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.10,0:01:53.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比纸更重要的东西就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.10,0:01:53.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even more important than the paper is
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.15,0:01:54.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:54.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the pencil
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.38,0:01:59.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铅笔可尖可钝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:59.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pencil is sharp or as dull as I like
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.02,0:02:00.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:00.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Funny
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.87,0:02:03.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我点子一多起来  你就缩小了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:03.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as my ideas grow, you shrink
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.26,0:02:08.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天写作文最美好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I couldn't have asked for
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a more beautiful day to write an essay
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.28,0:02:11.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  开始写了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:11.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.92,0:02:16.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,红绿灯前不能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:16.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"What Not To Do At A Stoplight"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.55,0:02:18.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还挺简单
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:18.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is easy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.85,0:02:21.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:21.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"By SpongeBob Squarepants"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.33,0:02:24.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这作文精华满满
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:24.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This essay is pure gold
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.02,0:02:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在呢  铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, pencil
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.45,0:02:26.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好开始动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:26.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get ready to do your stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.85,0:02:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为要开始写了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because here we go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:40.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(792,886)}红绿灯前不能做的事\N海绵宝宝作
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比我想得还要难
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is harder than I thought
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.12,0:02:57.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:57.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要立法禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It should be against the law
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.52,0:03:05.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这种阳光明媚的日子被迫写作文
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:01.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to have to write an essay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:05.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on such a super sailorific, sunshiny day
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.78,0:03:08.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我必须做下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:08.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I must press onward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.55,0:03:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为只要有这支铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because with this pencil
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再把作文写完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the completion of this essay
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.92,0:03:15.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就能离我驾照更近一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:15.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be one step closer to my driver's license
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这应该不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This'll be no problemo
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我时间还不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I got plenty of time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在才六点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's only 6:00
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.30,0:03:34.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:34.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.70,0:03:36.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  开始写了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:36.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,okay, here we go
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.17,0:03:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始写了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we go
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了  我只要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know, I just need to
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把体内的血液泵到脑袋里就行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get a little blood pumpin' in the old noodle
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做点健美操怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about some calisthenics?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感受到血脉在偾张了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can feel those juices pumpin' now
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.65,0:04:22.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:22.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须得写作文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to write that paper
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, pencil
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.67,0:04:29.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,写字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:29.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,make words
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.52,0:04:31.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:31.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.19,0:04:35.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我最爱的蜗牛近来可好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:35.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, how's my favorite mollusk?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要让海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about you let ol' SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你来点吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fix you up something to eat?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.07,0:04:42.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说你不饿是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:42.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, you're not hungry?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.46,0:04:46.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道我还得写作文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:46.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know I have an essay to write
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now come on, Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:57.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,962)}小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:54.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(486,444)}蜗牛粮
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.26,0:04:59.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得确保你补充到营养了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:59.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to make sure you get your nutrition
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.16,0:05:02.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你不吃光  我就不走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:02.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I'm not leaving until you eat every single bite
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你确定你不想要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, a-are you sure you don't want
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.96,0:05:10.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来点焦糖布丁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:10.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,some crème brulée?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.17,0:05:12.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不想要巧克力味海草块吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:12.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or-or some chocoflavored algae bits?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗搞得好乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary sure made a mess
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.15,0:05:17.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可写不了作文
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:17.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't work on my essay
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都得怪厨房乱糟糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,knowing there's a mess in the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺便把地板其他地方也打扫一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I might as well clean the rest of the floor while I'm at it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.56,0:05:36.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卫生死角也得打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:36.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should get these hard-to-reach places, too
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,盘子得洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And these dishes need to be cleaned
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.75,0:05:40.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏垃圾可不能有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:40.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't have dirty garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在应该够干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I think it's clean enough now
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也没花多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, that didn't take too long
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.85,0:05:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's only
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.65,0:05:51.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十点钟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:51.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,10:00
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.59,0:05:55.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能再乱混了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:55.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more fooling around
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.05,0:05:56.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须继续用功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:56.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to get back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  作文先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mr. Essay
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.88,0:06:00.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:00.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.12,0:06:03.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好让我写你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:03.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,prepare to be written
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.19,0:06:08.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在写了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:08.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.31,0:06:09.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在写了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:09.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.14,0:06:10.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:10.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.71,0:06:11.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:11.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.42,0:06:12.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再一点这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:12.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And some of these
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.15,0:06:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再一点这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and some of these
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快好了  然后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost there and
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.14,0:06:17.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:17.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,done
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.99,0:06:20.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看目前为止写得怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:20.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's see how it looks so far
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.00,0:06:23.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:23.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(846,358)}夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.48,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 无实义 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.76,0:06:26.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休息时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:26.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Break time
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走来走去有助于思考
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pacing always helps me think
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.38,0:06:31.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想  只剩799个字了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:31.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see, only 799 words to go
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  快点想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think, SpongeBob, think
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.34,0:06:42.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:42.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,W-Who's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.22,0:06:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.65,0:06:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, what you up to?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sleeping
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是太迷人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's really fascinating
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你睡得好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you having a good sleep?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.22,0:06:52.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不交流一下你做了什么梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:52.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any dreams you'd like to discuss?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.75,0:06:53.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:53.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember on the
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.47,0:06:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.83,0:06:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你我都知道你只是在利用我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You and I both know that you're just using me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让自己分心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as a distraction
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.42,0:07:00.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样你就暂时用不着写作文了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:00.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you don't have to write your essay
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这话不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is not true
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我打电话是想跟你谈个引人入胜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I called to have an engaging conversation with you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说我听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm listening
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Marco
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.49,0:07:12.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波罗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:12.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Polo
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.97,0:07:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就挂了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,well I got to get going, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有篇特重要的作文得写
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got an important essay to write
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也太爱聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a chatterbox
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.17,0:07:21.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他难道听不出来我很忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:21.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't he see that I'm busy?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.80,0:07:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纸上一堆橡皮屑  这样可写不了作文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:25.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't write with all these eraser shavings
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all over my paper
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,橡皮屑飘得我思维空间到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now they're floating around my thinking space
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  讨厌的小屑屑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, pesky particles
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.92,0:07:40.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我吞了一粒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:40.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I swallowed one
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.69,0:07:41.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呛到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:41.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm choking
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.06,0:07:42.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:42.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Water
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.10,0:07:44.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:44.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Water
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚才真是好险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a close one
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说大惊小怪是什么意思  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean overly dramatic, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.11,0:07:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚才呛的那口让我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All that choking sure made me hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不能饿着肚子就写作文  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't write on an empty stomach, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.02,0:08:03.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得补充一点精神食粮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:03.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to have my brain food
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要白面包还是黑面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,white or rye bread?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.74,0:08:08.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是黑麦粗面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:08.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or pumpernickel?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.57,0:08:11.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该得看里面夹的是什么肉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:11.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess it really depends on the meat inside
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.75,0:08:12.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:12.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A visitor?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.17,0:08:16.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:16.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:22.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1024,868)}邮件
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.67,0:08:20.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,寄给海绵宝宝先生的包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:20.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Package for Mr. Squarepants
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.72,0:08:22.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:22.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.46,0:08:24.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:24.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你喜欢送信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you like delivering mail?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.23,0:08:27.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我的饭碗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:27.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It puts bread on the table
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碗里是白面包还是黑麦粗面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rye or pumpernickel?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说你自己的信是自己送的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, do you deliver your own mail
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是说你有自己的邮递员会给你送
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or do you have your own mailperson?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是谁来送他的信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But then who delivers his mail?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.97,0:08:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是有没完没了一长串的邮递员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is there a never-ending chain of mailmen
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.17,0:08:41.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,互相在给其他邮递员送信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:41.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,delivering mail to other mailmen?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.10,0:08:43.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我估计邮筒理论上能断掉这串关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess a P.O. box
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,could, in theory break the chain
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是还得写作文吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a paper to write?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.21,0:08:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他怎么知道我应该得写作文
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did he know I'm supposed to be writing an essay?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.85,0:08:55.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其他消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:55.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In other news
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(498,550)}突发新闻
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.76,0:08:59.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本地居民海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:59.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,local resident SpongeBob Squarepants
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.45,0:09:02.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完成作文的时间仅剩数小时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:02.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,only has a few hours left to complete his essay
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.35,0:09:05.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且他仍在偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:05.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and yet he continues to goof off
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.45,0:09:07.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他何时才会做功课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:07.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When will he learn?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.95,0:09:13.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:13.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.83,0:09:17.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来  坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:17.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, take a seat
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.57,0:09:20.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把脚放上来  放松一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:20.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put your feet up and relax
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.21,0:09:25.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:25.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.45,0:09:26.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,半夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:26.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Midnight
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.63,0:09:30.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:30.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.42,0:09:30.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:30.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.85,0:09:32.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到书桌前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:32.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,back to desk
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.83,0:09:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚才真是好险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a close call
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My pants
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.04,0:09:42.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:42.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你给我上来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You get up here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还得写作文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to get back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.02,0:09:45.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:45.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Freedom
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤子别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop, pants
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.21,0:09:49.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你马上给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:49.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You get back here this instant
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.19,0:09:50.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:50.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pants
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.15,0:10:01.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间到了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:10:01.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time's up, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Burning
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.31,0:10:08.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只剩799个字了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:08.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only 799 words to go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.58,0:10:11.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:11.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.92,0:10:16.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:16.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命  我家着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help, my house is on fire
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.85,0:10:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, why?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.02,0:10:31.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你为什么要放火烧我  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:31.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did you set me on fire, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.65,0:10:34.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么不写作文
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:34.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just write your essay?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.64,0:10:37.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别浪费时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:37.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop wasting time
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我作文在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's my essay?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.85,0:10:43.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:43.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.30,0:10:46.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定是睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:46.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must have dozed off
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看  写到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:49.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(784,380)}夫
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.17,0:10:52.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敢不敢看看几点了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:52.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I dare look at the clock?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快九点了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's almost 9:00
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.25,0:10:59.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五分钟后就要上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:10:59.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Class starts in five minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.97,0:11:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我五分钟怎么写得完一整篇作文
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How am I going to write this whole paper in five minutes?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.05,0:11:06.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么知道红绿灯前不能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:06.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to know what not to do at a stoplight?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.98,0:11:10.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,红绿灯前不能喂蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:08.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feeding your snail
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is something not to do at a stoplight
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.10,0:11:15.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不能做三明治  也不能点蜡烛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:15.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and making a sandwich and-and lighting candles
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.06,0:11:17.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不能喝水  也不能打电话找朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:17.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and drinking water and calling your friends
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不能劈电视
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and karate chopping the TV
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.58,0:11:20.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不能跟邮递员闲聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:20.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and shooting the breeze with the mailman
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.09,0:11:21.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不能睡着  也不能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:21.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and falling asleep and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:22.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(580,382)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.92,0:11:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  我写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, I'm finished
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八百字全写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All 800 words
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm finished
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.76,0:11:31.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:31.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it is
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.65,0:11:32.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:32.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.52,0:11:35.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:35.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.73,0:11:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.45,0:11:38.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要交给你  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:38.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八百字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,800 words
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主题是红绿灯及红绿灯前不能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all about stoplights and what not to do at them
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.76,0:11:45.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我之前给你打过电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:45.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I tried to call you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.92,0:11:48.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去参加教研会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:48.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to go to a teachers' convention
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我作文怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what about my essay?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我决定要取消作业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I decided to cancel the assignment
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.34,0:11:57.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,改去红绿灯前实地考察
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:54.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're just going to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:57.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,take a field trip to a stoplight instead
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下周再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you next week
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:08.04,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,313)}我和傻瓜\N{\fs20} \N{\fs150}在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:12.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19\pos(398,610)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19\pos(294,330)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.27\pos(448,312)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.95\pos(288,322)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz21.2\pos(446,662)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.92,0:12:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扫  扫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweep, sweep
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.18,0:12:33.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:33.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Need
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,furniture
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.81,0:12:47.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你干嘛在做装修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:47.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what's with the home improvement?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.94,0:12:52.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:52.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.88,0:12:53.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扫  扫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:53.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweep, sweep
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我过来是要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Patrick, I came over to see
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.25,0:12:58.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不想去捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:58.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you wanted to go jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过看得出来你一直在忙自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I can see you're busy having an episode
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know something, Spongebob?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只想着玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's just all fun and games for you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.95,0:13:08.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么都跟你没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:08.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing really matters
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们去捉水母吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Let's go jelly fishing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们什么都不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"We don't have any work to do
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.52,0:13:16.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生活就像一大碗精制什锦腰果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:16.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Life is just a big bowl of fancy, assorted cashews
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.92,0:13:20.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都用不着掸灰  用不着清理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"and nobody has anything to dust or to clean
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用不着擦干净  用不着瞎编
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or to wipe, or fabricate"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.48,0:13:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只见过你清理盘子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the only thing I've ever seen you clean is your plate
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.67,0:13:35.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么办  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:35.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.01,0:13:37.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:37.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got to help me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.42,0:13:39.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你又忘了怎么吃东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:39.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you forgot how to eat again
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.57,0:13:41.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧  拿漏斗来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:41.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, we'll get the funnel
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.02,0:13:42.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是那回事  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:42.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.23,0:13:44.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有更严重的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:44.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's worse
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还挺喜欢漏斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn, I like the funnel
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.84,0:13:46.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事那么严重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:46.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what is it then?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.90,0:13:47.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:47.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.80,0:13:50.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一张字条
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:50.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A note
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:50.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(776,920)}音 符
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  可你再看背面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but turn it over
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.82,0:13:53.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有封信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:53.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a letter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:53.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(780,920)}字母
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.56,0:13:55.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:55.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.35,0:13:58.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我还收到了我爸妈的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:58.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I got this message from my parents
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你爸妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your parents?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的派大星  我和你妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Dear Patrick, Your mom and I
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天要来过海星节了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"are coming out tomorrow for Starfish Day
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽量想起来  不过别想太用力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Please try to remember, but don't try too hard
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然又会像上次那样受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"or you'll hurt yourself like last time
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱你的  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Love, Daddy"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.85,0:14:12.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我爸妈觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:12.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, my parents think
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我比一大袋尿布还要笨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm dumber than a sack of diapers
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是这样  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, they don't, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸妈就喜欢玩激将法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Parents just like to push your buttons
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(878,920)}按 钮
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.55,0:14:18.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:18.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like this--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么玩总能让我振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That always cheers me up
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.33,0:14:24.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可今天不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:24.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But not today
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.71,0:14:27.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  要是你爸妈觉得你很笨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:27.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, if your parents think you're dumb
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那他们肯定不知道真笨是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then they must not know what dumb really is
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.67,0:14:31.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可他们不看电视的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:31.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But don't they watch television?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就是我意思  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.65,0:14:35.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你爸妈见到了个真笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:35.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If your parents got to meet a real dummy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.91,0:14:38.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那他们就会发现你有多天才了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:38.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they'd realize what genius you really are
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.70,0:14:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可灯神不是住灯里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But don't genius live in a lamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:40.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(512,920)}天 才
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且我们也不认识笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And besides, we don't know any dumb people
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来当笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be the dummy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.72,0:14:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等到你爸妈看到我表现有多笨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When your parents see how dumb I act
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们就会当你是史上最聪明的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they'll think you're the smartest guy ever
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.42,0:14:53.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,数学力量大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:53.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Math is power
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,ABCD
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A, B, C, D
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,EFG
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,E, F, G
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,HIJKLMNO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,H, I, J, K, L, M, N, O
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是得再拿喇叭出来  马蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Should I get the bullhorn again, Marty?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.67,0:15:03.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,WXYZ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:03.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,W, X, Y and Z?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.10,0:15:05.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:05.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.02,0:15:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸爸好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿子  你这次认得我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Son, you recognized us this time
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么就不认得我自己的亲生父母了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't I recognize my own parents?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你脑子一直不是很灵光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You never were a bright one
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不来带我们参观一下你家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, aren't you going to show us inside?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可能都忘了家在哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He probably forgot where it is
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know where
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.63,0:15:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来带路  这样才不会迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me lead the way so we don't get lost, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.35,0:15:25.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手牵手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:25.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold hands now
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.27,0:15:29.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  就快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:29.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,数到三放手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let go on three
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.55,0:15:31.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:31.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.37,0:15:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.17,0:15:34.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:34.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good job
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拍拍派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pats for Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.77,0:15:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去拿饮料来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll go get the beverages
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.48,0:15:47.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:47.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Son
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这回把饮料拿东西装起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You put the drinks in something this time
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.80,0:15:53.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿子  你一定整晚都在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:53.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Son, you must've been working all night
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.15,0:15:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为我们好好打理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to put these together for us
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We love you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁  白痴来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray, the idiot's here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.84,0:16:02.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  我来开门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:02.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'll get it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.42,0:16:03.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,防护头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:03.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Protective helmet--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.57,0:16:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,check
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.08,0:16:07.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就该这么扮傻的  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:07.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to look stupid, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.89,0:16:09.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会出差错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:09.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What could go wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.62,0:16:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太惊喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.82,0:16:12.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:12.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸  妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom, Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.92,0:16:15.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认识下我邻居  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:15.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,meet my neighbor, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.04,0:16:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.17,0:16:18.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:18.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello there
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.46,0:16:19.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:19.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.72,0:16:20.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:20.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.92,0:16:22.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,握个手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:22.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put her there
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:22.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(710,920)}放 上 来
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mama, Mama
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说的是握手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He means shake
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(846,920)}摇 晃
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Spongebob, no
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,握的是手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shake hands
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(614,920)}摇
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住我爸的手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grab my dad's hand
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.07,0:16:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只用一只手抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grab it with only one hand
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good boy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.27,0:16:43.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再上下动你的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:43.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now move your arm up and down
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.27,0:16:47.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:47.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你住在附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,do you live nearby?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.15,0:16:49.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:49.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.02,0:16:51.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:51.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.40,0:16:53.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给他们看看你家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:53.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show them your house
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是女式衬衫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, not your blouse
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.30,注释,,0,0,0,,[ blouse（女式衬衫）与 house（房子）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.30,0:16:57.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:57.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your house
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他住水果里的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He lives in a fruit?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太不健康了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's unhealthy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.82,0:17:10.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:10.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.70,0:17:13.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来共进晚餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:13.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to stay for dinner?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.02,0:17:21.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他吃完东西都会那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:21.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does he always do that after he eats?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就星期三那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only on Wednesday
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.48,0:17:33.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你朋友可能脑子坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:33.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I think your friend might be broken
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.03,0:17:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  而且得用不少遮蔽胶带
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:36.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and it would take more than some masking tape
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.50,0:17:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才可以修好他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to fix that guy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.90,0:17:44.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不会有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:44.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he going to be okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.58,0:17:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们应该看他每天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You should see him in the morning
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,边跳边喊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,prancing around, yelling
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.15,0:17:52.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:52.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.42,0:17:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把邻居全逼疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He drives all the neighbors crazy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.75,0:17:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先前有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.75,0:17:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, just the other day
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.65,0:17:58.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们邻居章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:58.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,our neighbor Squidward was
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.10,0:18:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他根本没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's really no help for him
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.30,0:18:06.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们看他的衣着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:06.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, look at the way he's dressed
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有脑袋钻了洞的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only somebody with holes drilled in their head
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才会这么穿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would wear that stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有这形状怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And how about this shape?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.91,0:18:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听说过胸肌发达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, I've heard of barrel-chested
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可没听说过胸肌发方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but never box-chested
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.82,0:18:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.24,0:18:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能不能找你借睫毛膏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,do you have any mascara I could borrow?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.19,0:18:30.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那男孩子还化妆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:30.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The boy wears makeup?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a card
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.17,0:18:42.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他喊了我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:42.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He said my name
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.87,0:18:45.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么把他训到那种程度的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:45.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How'd you train him to do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.93,0:18:49.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他咬我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:49.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He bit me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  来厨房找我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, meet me in the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.35,0:18:56.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨蛋大概是想找我私下聊聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:56.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess the dummy wants to have a private conversation
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.98,0:19:00.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,聊的是笨话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:00.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A dumb one
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what's on your mind?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.69,0:19:05.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:05.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经知道你什么问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I already know the answer
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.32,0:19:08.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:08.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧  可好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, that's funny
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.37,0:19:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你就是笨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause you're dumb
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.72,0:19:15.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  能不能尽量少侮辱我一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:13.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, could you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:15.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let up on the insults just a little bit?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.77,0:19:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚那些给你整不会了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're those too complicated for you?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尽量试试傻瓜化一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll try dumbing them down a bit
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.60,0:19:24.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我感觉你真觉得我笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:22.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I get the feeling that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you think I really am dumb
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:27.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(760,512)}我和笨蛋在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.07,0:19:30.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就等你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:30.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just what I'd expect you to say
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.14,0:19:33.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨蛋就是完全不会发现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:33.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dumb people are always blissfully unaware
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.95,0:19:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己有多笨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of how dumb they really are
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.02,0:19:40.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这只是在装笨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:40.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm only pretending to be dumb
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我们计划  记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was our plan, remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.17,0:19:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  要是你能看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spongebob, if only you could see
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说的话有多笨就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how stupid you sound right now
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.65,0:19:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还非得高谈阔论幻想出来的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with your talk of imaginary plans
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说吧  你让我心情特别好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell you what, you've caught me in a good mood
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.63,0:19:55.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就顺从你一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:55.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll humor you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.44,0:19:55.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:55.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go on
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.95,0:19:59.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快出去给大家表现聪明点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:59.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go out there and act smart for everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.45,0:20:00.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:00.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I will
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.58,0:20:03.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:03.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And-and don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.85,0:20:05.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会帮你捂热的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:05.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll keep this warm for you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我摊牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a confession to make
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.57,0:20:11.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚做的傻事都是骗你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:11.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lied about being stupid
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.82,0:20:13.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是在装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:13.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just acted like a fool
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样你们才能再稍微多重视派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you would appreciate Patrick a little bit more
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.87,0:20:17.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会说话  会吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:17.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know how to talk and eat
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.90,0:20:18.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还会洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:18.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and do laundry--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.92,0:20:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还分得清黑白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I even separate the darks and the lights
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.02,0:20:23.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我们就从头来过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:23.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So what do you say we start over and try again
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.15,0:20:26.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:26.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name is Spongebob Squarepants
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我不笨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I am not a dummy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.63,0:20:30.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:30.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.78,0:20:32.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在厨房待上个三分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:32.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three minutes in the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.32,0:20:33.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们儿子就教会他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:33.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and our son has taught him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.54,0:20:35.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用完整的句子说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:35.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to talk in complete sentences
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.91,0:20:37.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好样的  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:37.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good work, son
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.02,0:20:38.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这趟不容易  爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:38.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It wasn't easy, Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.02,0:20:40.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可可可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:40.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,B-but-but
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.51,0:20:43.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你现在又得上说话课了  年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:43.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's time for your next lesson, young man
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now listen to me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不笨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not dumb
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.52,0:20:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a brain
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看  这是照片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, here's a picture of it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想必本来就那么大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That must be actual size
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.78,0:20:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.92,0:21:00.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我大脑大小正常  功能也正常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:00.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's normal size and fully functional
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.44,0:21:01.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:01.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.29,0:21:05.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二加二等于四
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:05.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two plus two equals four
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.75,0:21:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿子  你还教了他数学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, son, you taught him math, too
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还教了他唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you taught him to sing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.37,0:21:15.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在他短路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:15.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now he's short-circuiting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.52,0:21:17.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是你把他教过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:17.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must've taught him a little too much
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.71,0:21:44.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿子  你要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:44.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, son
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.87,0:21:47.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我心里一直清楚你的智力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:47.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've always known that when it comes to brightness
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.47,0:21:50.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就跟三瓦灯泡的亮度差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:50.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,well, you're about a three-watt
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.68,0:21:51.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是这位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:51.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But this guy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.90,0:21:54.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就是漆黑洞穴里点不着的湿火柴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:54.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's a wet match in a dark cave
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.00,0:21:57.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,显得接线员都比他聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:57.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He makes phone operators seem smart
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.19,0:21:59.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿子  不过更重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.19,0:21:59.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But more importantly, son
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.77,0:22:02.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他让我明白了你现在变得有多聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:00.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's shown me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:02.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what a sharp, quick-witted boy you've become
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.22,0:22:05.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉现在我才算是真正认识了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:05.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I-I feel like I'm really meeting you for the first time
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.25,0:22:08.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说对吧  珍妮特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:08.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Janet?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.41,0:22:10.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了  马蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:10.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You bet, Marty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.20,0:22:12.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍妮特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:12.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Janet?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.80,0:22:13.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.80,0:22:13.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Marty?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.40,0:22:16.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:16.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.42,0:22:17.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马蒂  我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:17.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Marty, I'm scared
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.37,0:22:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.37,0:22:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.55,0:22:23.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可爱的夫妇俩是你家的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.55,0:22:23.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does this lovely couple belong to you?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.45,0:22:25.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们站在我家外面喊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.45,0:22:25.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They've been standing outside my house saying
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.37,0:22:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星在哪  已经一整天了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.37,0:22:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Where's Patrick?" all day
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.07,0:22:28.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快让我烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:28.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's driving me nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.07,0:22:29.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:29.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.42,0:22:31.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:31.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.90,0:22:36.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿子  你这次认得我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:36.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Son, you actually recognized us this time
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.85,0:22:39.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且你今天还记得穿衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.85,0:22:39.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you remembered to get dressed today
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.97,0:22:48.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.97,0:22:48.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, honey
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.17,0:22:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们没生儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we don't have a son
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.87,0:22:51.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.87,0:22:51.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
